# 🎲 DiceX - Modern Dice Game

A modern and responsive Dice Game built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Docker, GitHub Actions, and AWS EC2**.

The game features smooth animations, realistic dice faces, sound effects, history tracking, and automatic deployment using CI/CD.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎲 Interactive Dice Roll
- 🎨 Modern Glassmorphism UI
- 📱 Fully Responsive Design
- 🔊 Dice Roll Sound Effect
- 📜 Roll History Panel
- ⚡ Smooth Animations
- 🖱️ Click Anywhere to Roll
- 🐳 Docker Support
- ☁️ AWS EC2 Deployment
- 🚀 GitHub Actions Auto Deploy

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Docker
- Nginx
- GitHub Actions
- AWS EC2
- Git

