## 🖥️ Local Setup

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/princegoti13/dice-game.git
```

Go to project folder

```bash
cd dice-game
```

Run locally

Just open

```
index.html
```

or use Live Server in VS Code.

---

## 🐳 Docker

Build Image

```bash
docker build -t dice-game .
```

Run Container

```bash
docker run -d \
--name dice-game \
-p 9091:80 \
dice-game
```

---

## ☁️ Deployment

The application is deployed on:

- AWS EC2
- Docker
- Nginx

Every push to the **main** branch automatically deploys the latest version using GitHub Actions.

